"Monuments of Condolence","quest_id":125000110},{"text":"Nice to meet you. I'm Santong, and this is my grandpa.","quest_name":"Monuments of Condolence","quest_id":125000110},{"text":"I asked my grandpa where he went every day, and he mentioned meeting up with his old friends.","quest_name":"Monuments of Condolence","quest_id":125000110},{"text":"Only now do I realize he's been coming here daily! I just wanted to convince him to return to Jinzhou, but he wouldn't listen. So frustrating!","quest_name":"Monuments of Condolence","quest_id":125000110},{"text":"I hope he hasn't caused you any trouble. I apologize on behalf of my grandpa.","quest_name":"Monuments of Condolence","quest_id":125000110},{"text":"Thank you so much. I'm trying to persuade him to go home and get proper treatment, hoping it will help him recover sooner.","quest_name":"Monuments of Condolence","quest_id":125000110},{"text":"Oh no, I'm really sorry! I'm trying to persuade him to go home and get proper treatment, hoping it will help him recover sooner.","quest_name":"Monuments of Condolence","quest_id":125000110},{"text":"Grandpa, now that the flowers are delivered, how about we head back home?","quest_name":"Monuments of Condolence","quest_id":125000110},{"text":"Stop being stubborn, grandpa! You’re trying to enter a military facility! You're no longer in service and you’re obstructing the military officers!","quest_name":"Monuments of Condolence","quest_id":125000110},{"text":"...","quest_name":"Monuments of Condolence","quest_id":125000110},{"text":"Alright, as long as you're happy...","quest_name":"Monuments of Condolence","quest_id":125000110},{"text":"But, if you can't find your way home or cause any trouble for the soldiers or Patrollers, no matter what you say, I'll take you home, okay?","quest_name":"Monuments of Condolence","quest_id":125000110}]}